title: Jetobatics
brief_description: We meet the four Royal New Zealand Air Force pilots who form New Zealand’s team of jet plane aerobats and travel in their Vampire jet aircraft while they give a magnificent display of high speed aerobatics and smoke pattern making in the sky.
